			<abstract>
				<p>Testimony of 19-year-old G.J. and 18-year-old G.R. on their experiences as members of the commando “Kanada” in Birkenau, and slave
					labor in the Reichenbach, Porta Fallersleben, and Salzwedel camps.</p>
			</abstract>
